<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Iniciar Sesión</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../pub/stylesheets/bootstrap.css">  
    <script src="./public/javascripts/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>  
    <div class="">             
        <div class="row vh-100">            
            <div class="col col-5">
                <img src="./public/images/loginLogo.jpg" class="logo" alt="">               
                <div class="container p-5 mx-5 mt-4">
                    <p class="h2 mt-4 text-primary t-color">Explore y conéctese con otros a través de pasatiempos mutuos</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary py-1 mt-5">Bienvenido! Por favor inicia sesión.</p>

                    <form action="">
                        <div class="mb-1">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label"> Correo electronico</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control text-primary">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">                        
                            <label for="password" class="form-label">Contraseña</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control">                        
                        </div>                                     
                        <div class="mt-3 d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" name="" id="">
                                <span class="form-check-label">Recordar contraseña</span>
                            </div>                       
                            <span><a href="#" class="link-secondary">¿Olvidaste la contraseña?</a></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-3 d-flex justify-content-left">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Ingresar</button>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary mx-4">Registrarse</a>
                        </div>
                    
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col gb">
            </div>
          
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

<style>  
    .gb{
        background-image: url("../public/images/login-blue-background.jpg");
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        margin-left: 6rem;
    }

    .logo{
        position: absolute;
        height: 150px;
        width: auto;
        z-index: -1;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .t-color{
        color: #015f9a !important;
    }
 
</style>
</html>